video.title: CV1 11:30/11:31 pace to Dracula
video.description: Just a really good run I got out of nowhere that couldn't finish. I got the 2-cycle pattern but missed the turnaround jump. Later on in the same stream I got an 11:32/11:33 pace that I lost to the same reason.  This at least gives me confidence that I can get a much better time much sooner than I expected.
